items.title: Live updates: Trump says U.S. and Iran will meet next week
items.description: A ceasefire agreed to by Israel and Iran appears to be holding after it was announced by President Donald Trump.

items.title: Trump speaks at NATO press conference
items.description: President Donald Trump's comments come days after he announced a ceasefire in the war between Israel and Iran.

items.title: 'Time to get serious on defense': A moment of truth for NATO as leaders seek unity on spending hike
items.description: NATO members have been facing pressure, particularly from ally Washington, to more than double their defense spending target.

items.title: Greece is one of NATO's top defense spenders. Here's why
items.description: Greece has consistently been one of NATO's top defense spenders, with its tense relationship with Turkey being a key factor in this policy.

items.title: Trump to Congress: 'NO ONE GOES ON VACATION' until spending bill passes
items.description: President Donald Trump's pressure comes as the bill still faces an uphill climb ahead of Republicans' self-imposed July 4 deadline.
